description: While reading a book a read about keeping a knolage portfolio. I liked this idea, but it was talking figuratively.
title: This Website: Made Using React, Node.js, and Firebase
tldr: This project is the website you are currently on. I was made using React, Next.js, and Firebase. It took just over a week of active time working on It. It is fully reactive to work on mobile and other small devices. It has a contact me page (samueldoes.dev/contact), posts projects (samueldoes.dev/projects), and even a interactive 3d model (samueldoes.dev), All made with React. Source Code on the github, and you are currently seeing the live demo.
